    "description":  "How to contact HMRC if you’re a large business with a general or non-technical query.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"call-to-action\"\u003e\n  \u003cp\u003eIf you’re a large business with a technical query, you should contact your designated \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/hm-revenue-and-customs-large-business\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eCustomer Compliance Manager\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-contact-us-by-email\"\u003eHow to contact us by email\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eUse this list of email addresses to contact us if you have a general, non-technical query. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou’ll need your 3-digit tax office code number to find the correct email address. You can find this number on all the correspondence from your Corporation Tax office. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eTax office code number\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eEmail address\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e005\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinessnorthwest@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinessnorthwest@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e054\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinessmidlands@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinessmidlands@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e163\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinesslondon@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinesslondon@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e268\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinesslondon@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinesslondon@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e294\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinessnortheast@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinessnortheast@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e349\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinessscotlandandni@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinessscotlandandni@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e572\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinessmidlands@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinessmidlands@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e660\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinesssouthandwales@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinesssouthandwales@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e834\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinessscotlandandni@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinessscotlandandni@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e854\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:contactus.largebusinessscotlandandni@hmrc.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003econtactus.largebusinessscotlandandni@hmrc.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
